name: TellSomeoneThey'reAwesome
0:
”Alexa, you're awesome.”
”Tell Brenda she's awesome.”
”Tell Frank he's awesome.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: you're awesome
des:
SAY: Alexa, you're awesome
When asked who's awesome
SAY: (someone's name)
 OR
SAY: Tell (someone's name) (he's, she's, they're) awesome
 OR
SAY: Help for the help response
 OR
SAY: (quiet, cancel) to silence Alexa and end the session quietly
 OR
SAY: (end, stop, thanks, thank you) to end the session normally
 OR
SAY (quit) to immediately exit the skill
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
